              ###  Are there better approaches?




 Yes, they are better approaches. for instance, if i combine my code and the AI assited code, i will get another code 

```py
while True:
    word = input("Enter a word (or 'exit'): ")
    
    if word.lower() == 'exit':
        break
        
    word = "".join(c.lower() for c in word if c.isalnum())

    if word == word[::-1]:
        print("Yes, it is a palindrome")
    else:
        print("No, it is not")

print("Goodbye, Have a great day.")

